                        <p><em>Adaír Necalli is a rising junior at Duke studying Linguistics and Child Policy. Their research focuses on indigenous language revitalization. They would like to thank Norma de Jesus, David Preston, Attyat Mayans, Gabriela Asturias, Ashley Claw, Taylor Miller, and the Native American Student Alliance students pictured in the photo collage in this article for helping make this endeavor a reality.&nbsp;</em></p>
